snippet.title: Zack Snyder Confirms: "We Will Not Fire Amber Heard From Aquaman 2!"
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 Filmmakers Will NOT Cut Amber Heard from Film Despite Urging of Johnny Depp fans, says Producer Zack Snyder.

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

Despite millions of Johnny Depp fans trying their hardest, Amber Heard will not be removed from Aquaman 2 according to a producer working on the sequel. Amber Heard is the ex-wife of Depp, who had a large case with him over abuse accusations, ending recently with Heard winning the main case, with Depp winning an appeal recently to further investigate other claims. 

#AmberHeard #ZackSnyder #Aquaman2
